emuInput.TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Shelia Christian wearing a light colored beaded cardigan, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Barbara Winters wearing a light colored sheer blouse with lace and ruffle trim, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 24, 1956, pg. A26 reads: "Teen Queen Contest Going Great - With the 1956 Hill Top Teen Queen contest getting into its stride..."
